\newlabel{fig:null_profile}{{13}{17}{Null test: extinction profile resulting from cross-correlating a ``foreground'' sample of redMaGiC hi-z galaxies ($z > 0.65$) with reddening of actual foreground galaxies with $z<0.45$ taken from the high-density sample. Excess around 200 kpc and at $r > 10 Mpc$ are noticeable; otherwise, the curve is consistent with zero}{figure.13}{}}
