\newlabel{fig:fgr_vs_not}{{14}{17}{Extinction profiles, with and without subtraction of the random-foreground real-background cross-correlation signal. The fully random-subtracted galaxy-\av correlations are shown in teal; the correlation without foreground random subtractions are shown in blue. An extinction profile calculated with a modified $A_V$ estimator is shown in dark blue in the left panel}{figure.14}{}}
