\newlabel{fig:avhist}{{15}{18}{Histogram of $A_V$ (the optimal estimator) for the redMaGiC catalogs. Estimator values for the high-luminosity high-redshift sample (calculated in 2, 5 and 9 redshift bins) are on the left; the distribution of the estimator values for the high-density sample (calculated with 3, 8, and 17 redshift bins) are on the right. The dotted black lines mark $A_V = 0$}{figure.15}{}}
